Log-Log4perl-Appender-Lim-CLI - A Log4perl appender for Lim CLI

ABOUT

This module is used for getting Log::Log4perl output to the Lim::CLI module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Log::Log4perl::Appender::Lim::CLI

You can also look for information at:

    Issue tracker (report bugs here)
        http://github.com/jelu/log-log4perl-appender-lim-cli/issues

    GIT repository
        http://github.com/jelu/log-log4perl-appender-lim-cli


